text: I'm not calling this an album since it only has 5 tracks. They're the older tracks I composed around 2007-2008. I unfortunately lost the source files except for Trippin', which is the only one I had the chance to remaster a bit. Strollin' is the practice music used in The Impossible Game (X360 version), which the guy doing Rage Quit from Rooster Teeth absolutely loved (http://youtu.be/_E96i-u_5E0?t=1m22s).
